game.description:
Are you stuck with traditional puzzle challenges? Do you want to try out something new and brain-storming? If yes, we have brought to you a brand new arcade challenge where you have to challenge your brain power to solve out each puzzle. Lots of hurdles and obstacles will be there to restrict you from moving forward and advancing to the next level. However, putting your good knowledge about the numbers and sound understanding about the puzzles will help to get you through multiple levels.

You should try out 100 game for sure especially if the alchemy, numbers as well as exterminating small and innocent creatures are the things of your choice. Take the charge of your own tower and get ready to eliminate your cauldron as well as flasks and vials while getting you prepared to witness the unique concoctions you have ever brewed. When you click the play button, you would find a board where multiple colored numbers with different figures are lying.

Your objective in this html5 puzzle challenge is to remove all the characters by creating a sum of 100. An advanced level, you would also find out the number with the subtraction sign. So, you can also decrease their figure after connecting with the other number with greater value.  Keep making a sum of 100 with two or more characters and clearing the board in each level! There are 60 unique and challenging levels to explore in this logical number brainteaser. Good luck boys to have fun without download on atmegame.com!
